Package: bestsubset
Title: Best Subset Selection via MIQP (Fixed k and Auto-EBIC)
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Edoardo", "Lanzetti", , "edoardo.lanzetti@epfl.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements an exact algorithm for Best Subset Selection in linear 
    regression using Mixed-Integer Quadratic Programming (MIQP) via the 'Gurobi' 
    optimizer. It supports fixed-size subset selection with Big-M constraints 
    and automatic model selection based on a validation set approach.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: 
    gurobi,
    Matrix
URL: https://github.com/tr3d0/bestsubset
